Movement, said that with the repeal of the 8th amendment, "the era
of clandestine governments" would be ended.
</P>
<P>
Parliamentary leader of Jamiat Ulema-e-Islam Muhammad Khan
Sherani said it is the prime duty of parliamentarians to protect
the constitution.  
