will be no compromise by any of our partners with the Congress
party leadership," Yadav said.
</P>
<P>
He said the front leadership had asked the Congress party to
reconsider its withdrawal of support to the UF government.
</P>
<P>
According to local press reports today, Congress party
President Sitaram Kesri had ruled out a review of the decision to
withdraw support to the UF government in an interview on a local
television.  
