Zhu made the remark in talks this afternoon with Howard at the
Diaoyutai State Guesthouse.
</P>
<P>
Welcoming Howard and the Australian government officials and
businessmen in his delegation, Zhu pointed out that
Sino-Australian ties are oriented to the 21st century.
</P>
<P>
