Australia five years ago.
</P>
<P>
Expressing his pleasure at meeting with Zhu, Howard said that
never before has such a big business delegation accompanied an
Australian leader on a visit abroad. This shows that the
Australian government and business people are keen on developing
bilateral economic and trade cooperation, he said.
</P>
<P>
