<HEADLINE> Hang Seng China Enterprises Index Down </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HONG KONG, April 1 (Xinhua) -- Hang Seng China Enterprises
Index today fell 21.56 points to close at 944.07.
</P>
<P>
The Index, introduced in August 1995, tracks the overall
performance of China's 25 state enterprises listed on the Hong
Kong Stock Exchange.
</P>
<P>
Meanwhile today's Hang Seng MidCap 50 Index fell 46.08 points
from the previous session to close at 1,737.71.
</P>
