<TEXT>
<P>
ADDIS ABABA, April 1 (Xinhua) -- Eritrean president Isaias
Afwerki has laid a cornerstone for the construction of a
five-star hotel in Asmara, capital of Eritrea, the latest issue
of weekly English "Eritrea Profile" reported.
</P>
