already in Cape Town today, according to U.N. sources.
</P>
<P>
In recent months, envoys from the European Union, the United
States, Belgium, Kenya and South Africa attempted to negotiate a
ceasefire and peaceful settlement of the crisis in Zaire.
</P>
<P>
The Secretary-General appears to have asserted his authority to
have Sahnoun play the leading role in bringing an end to the civil
war in Zaire.
</P>
<P>
Sahnoun also represents the Organization of African Unity (OAU)
in Central Africa. 
