occurred in March of 1996. And last year's unprecedented flood
disasters destroyed more than crops on 730,000 ha and 250,000
rooms, and affected four million people.
</P>
<P>
Official statistics showed that direct economic losses amounted
to more than six billion yuan.
</P>
<P>
Relief funds came immediately from the central government and
rose from 20 million yuan in 1995 to 96 million yuan last year,
financing the reconstruction of more than 130 flood-destroyed
water conservancy facilities and over 50,000 new rooms. 
