<TEXT>
<P>
WASHINGTON, March 31 (Xinhua) -- Tenth seed Karina Habsudova of
Slovakia and 15th seed Elena Likhovtseva of Russia suffered
first-round defeats at the Hilton Head tennis tournament in Hilton
Head, South Carolina on Monday.
