<HEADLINE> Hingis Says She Deserves Top Spot </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
WASHINGTON, March 31 (Xinhua) -- Switzerland's Martina Hingis,
who became the youngest ever women's number one on Monday, said in
Hilton Head, South Carolina on Monday at the WTA tournament that
she fully deserved the ranking.
</P>
