<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Magnetic Card Telephones Becoming Popular in Nanjing </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
NANJING, April 1 (Xinhua) -- Nanjing, the capital of east
China's Jiangsu Province, has installed more than 500 magnetic
card telephone booths along the 44 streets in the city proper.
</P>
<P>
Some 1.5 million magnetic cards have been sold in the city,
with 50 million yuan (5.1 million U.S. dollars) of sales
value. The sales volume of the magnetic cards in Nanjing is more
than the combined total of Beijing, Shanghai and Tianjin.
</P>
<P>
Nanjing began to provide the magnetic card telephone service in
1993 and the business has maintained a steady growth. In 1993, the
number of magnetic card telephones only accounted for 1.5 percent
of the total public phones. Now they account for 17 percent of
the total.
</P>
<P>
The city now has 2,100 magnetic card telephone sets.
</P>
<P>
At the same time, the "card collection fever" has also given
rise to the widespread interest in the magnetic cards.
</P>
<P>
In 1995, a magnetic card with a picture of a pig, one of the 12
animals in the Chinese zodiac, had a face value of 50 yuan (5.1
dollars), and was sold for 45 yuan. There were not many buyers.
</P>
<P>
Now, however, the card is sold for as high as 1,500 (187
dollars) on the free market. The price of an "ox" card also went
up from 50 yuan to 350 yuan (43 dollars) only a month after its
issue at the beginning of this year. 
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> XIE19970401.0266 </DOCNO>
<DATE_TIME> 1997-04-01 </DATE_TIME>
<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Deschamps May Miss Friendly Due to Teething Problems </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
PARIS, March 31 (Xinhua) -- Dental problems may force Juventus
midfielder Didier Deschamps to miss France's friendly against
Sweden on Wednesday.
</P>
<P>
The injury worries over Deschamps, who has won the European Cup
with both Marseille and Juventus, were revealed at the French
training session on Monday by team director Jean-Marcel Ferret.
</P>
<P>
Paris Saint Germain striker Patrice Loko, the hat-trick hero
for his club in their Cup Winners Cup quarter-final triumph over
AEK Athens, has a left knee problem.
</P>
<P>
Barcelona defender Laurent Blanc is available although he did
not take part in the first training session for the Sweden game.
</P>
<P>
Aime Jacquet, the French coach, is expected to name his team on
Tuesday for the last friendly before the international tournament
in France in June, comprising Brazil, Italy, France and England.
</P>
