<HEADLINE> Israel Beat Luxembourg in World Cup Qualifier </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BRUSSELS, March 31 (Xinhua) -- Israel blanked hosts Luxembourg
3-0 in their World Cup qualifying match on Monday.
</P>
<P>
The win lifted Israel to the top spot in group five with 10
points from five games after Russia only managed a 1-1 draw in
Cyprus on Saturday.
</P>
<P>
